  <h2>Using ifloat<sup>®</sup></h2>
  <div class="first use_section">
    <p>We designed the site to be intuitive and have monitored the achievement of this since we launched. As a result we have made a number of changes to ensure we leverage the power of the data-driven application to the user's advantage.</p>
    <p>The power of the Find box is one of the gems of the site. The application has extensive and powerful algorithms to assist you and make helpful suggestions as to what we interpret your need to be, when there is not a clear match of words. The more words you type in the more focussed the result will be.</p>
    <p>The results of your Find will be the Categories that have any form of reference to your Find. When you select a Category, all the Product Types associated with you Find will display. On selection of a Product Type you will then have access to the unique and powerful product specification Filters that will quickly help you to find the products that are likely candidates for purchase. When you select Checkout, we will take you by a special link, to the Checkout on the website of one of our Partner Retailers for the normal payment process. Your purchase(s) will be shipped direct from  the Retailer to you.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="second use_section">
    <p>Where many products are possible solutions to your need, when the Product Detail page is displayed, simply click the 'Add to Compare List' button below the Basket. Keep doing this for as many products you require. When viewing your selection, the common properties are separated out leaving the differences clear to speed your choice.</p>
    <p>If you find a product and wish to save it for a Future Buy, then simply save it indefinitely by using the 'Add to Future Buys' button below the Basket. To use this feature we need you to Register with us so we can keep your list saved and separate.</p>
    <p>We welcome feedback; just send us an email via 'Contact Us'; all received are answered promptly.</p>
    <p>Thank you for reading about us and we hope to see you back soon.</p>
